VALUES(37, 9, 'Use Continuous Intelligence to Transform the Business', 'Continuous intelligence brings dramatic, measurable benefits in revenue generation, resource allocation, customer service and other metrics. More than ever, data and analytics leaders use real-time analytics to improve the performance of their businesses. Why is continuous intelligence proliferating now? What are best practices for deploying analytics into operations?', '2019-05-18 19:30:00.000+11', '2019-05-18 20:15:00.000+11', 'FFA', NULL, 0, '161 Sussex St, Sydney NSW 2000, Australia', 'https://www.google.ca/maps/place/Hyatt+Regency+Sydney/@-33.8700728,151.203584,15z/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x0:0xf782da6282a896be?ved=2ahUKEwjdqLCj4vfeAhUkWN8KHajtBzwQ_BIwCnoECAYQCA', NULL, 'https://www.gartner.com/en/conferences/apac/data-analytics-australia/agenda');
VALUES(38, 9, 'The Role of MDM in a Diverse IoT Landscape', 'IoT deployments tend to be one sensor for one measurement for a single purpose. But, data and analytics can enhance and expand the value of IoT to integrate data from many sensors and measurements with organizational and third-party data for a greater purpose. But, the ability to integrate data depends on the ability to unambiguously identify the IoT devices, correlate over the same time periods, and connect the data with each other in a meaningful way. This session will explain the role of MDM and the unique ways that has to be deployed in order to accomplish just that.

